MobilePayablesForecastingCardView is a CardView
    show labels
    main column
        Company
        Vendor
        PayablesInvoice.Invoice
            link is PayablesInvoiceNav
            raise blue alert when (OnHold)
                mouse over text is "<OnHoldMessage>_<PayablesInvoicePaymentsOnHoldRel.HoldCode>"
        DueDate
        DiscountDate
        PaymentAmount.CurrencyAmount
            label is "InvoiceAmount"
            total
